{"TopicDetails": {"type": 0, "ccm2Id": 45116536, "cftId": 0, "identifier": "ERASMUS-EDU-2022-POL-EXP-EUstatus", "title": "Pilot institutionalised EU cooperation instruments to explore the feasibility for a possible European legal status for alliances of higher education institutions", "publicationDateLong": 1655251200000, "callIdentifier": "ERASMUS-EDU-2022-POL-EXP-HE", "callTitle": "European policy experimentation in higher education", "callccm2Id": 45116549, "allowPartnerSearch": true, "workProgrammepart": {"id": 5995, "ccm_id": 44390830, "wp_part": "ERASMUS-2022", "wp_year": "ERASMUS-2022", "wp_title": "ERASMUS-2022", "wp_website": "https://erasmus-plus.ec.europa.eu/", "wp_document": "https://erasmus-plus.ec.europa.eu/resources-and-tools/documents-and-guidelines?"}, "frameworkProgramme": {"id": 43353764, "abbreviation": "ERASMUS2027", "description": "Erasmus+ Programme (ERASMUS)"}, "programmeDivision": [{"id": 43433291, "abbreviation": "PI-POLICY", "description": "Policy experimentations"}], "topicMGAs": [], "tags": ["legal status", "policy experimentation", "European Grouping of Territorial Cooperation (EGTC)", "European Universities alliances", "European Economic Interest Grouping (EEIG)"], "keywords": ["experimentation", "joint programmes"], "sme": false, "actions": [{"status": {"id": 31094503, "abbreviation": "Closed", "description": "Closed"}, "types": [{"typeOfAction": "ERASMUS-PJG ERASMUS Project Grants", "typeOfMGA": [{"id": 43341836, "abbreviation": "ERASMUS-AG", "description": "ERASMUS Action Grant Budget-Based"}]}], "plannedOpeningDate": "15 June 2022", "submissionProcedure": {"id": 31094504, "abbreviation": "single-stage", "description": "single-stage"}, "deadlineDates": ["06 October 2022"]}], "latestInfos": [], "budgetOverviewJSONItem": {"budgetTopicActionMap": {"3418423": [{"action": "ERASMUS-EDU-2022-POL-EXP-EUstatus - ERASMUS-PJG ERASMUS Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "15 June 2022", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["06 October 2022"], "budgetYearMap": {"2022": 1000000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}], "3418425": [{"action": "ERASMUS-EDU-2022-POL-EXP-EUdegree - ERASMUS-PJG ERASMUS Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "15 June 2022", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["06 October 2022"], "budgetYearMap": {"2022": 1000000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}]}, "budgetYearsColumns": ["2022"]}, "description": "<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">Scope</SPAN>:<p><em>Topic 2: Pilot institutionalised EU cooperation instruments to explore the feasibility for a possible European legal status for alliances of higher education institutions</em></p><p><em>Higher education alliances could benefit, on a voluntary basis, from institutionalised cooperation instruments, such as a possible legal status for alliances of higher education institutions, for example \u2018European Universities\u2019, that enable them to share human, technical, data, education, research and innovation capacities, where appropriate. This call will allow them to test, on a voluntary basis, existing European instruments, such as the European Grouping of Territorial Cooperation (EGTC) or the European Economic Interest Grouping (EEIG).</em></p>\n", "conditions": "<p><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">1.&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Eligible countries</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">:&nbsp;as described in the&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/erasmus/wp-call/2022/call-fiche_erasmus-edu-2022-pol-exp-he_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Call document</a><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">.</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#00B050;mso-fareast-language:&#10;EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">2.&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Eligibility and admissibility conditions:</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"> as described in the&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/erasmus/wp-call/2022/call-fiche_erasmus-edu-2022-pol-exp-he_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Call document</a><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Proposal page limits and layout:</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Please refer to Part B of the standard proposal template.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">3.&nbsp;&nbsp; Evaluation</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Evaluation criteria, scoring, threshold and process are described in the&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/erasmus/wp-call/2022/call-fiche_erasmus-edu-2022-pol-exp-he_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Call document</a><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:-.55pt;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">4.&nbsp;&nbsp; Indicative timetable for evaluation and grant agreement:</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"> as described in the&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/erasmus/wp-call/2022/call-fiche_erasmus-edu-2022-pol-exp-he_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px;\">Call document</a><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;&#10;text-indent:-.55pt;line-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Publication of the call:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 15 June 2022<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:&#10;-.55pt;line-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Deadline for submitting applications:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 6 October 2022 17:00 (Brussels local time)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:&#10;-.55pt;line-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Evaluation period:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;October 2022 - January 2023<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:&#10;-.55pt;line-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Information to applicants:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Mid - January 2023<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:&#10;-.55pt;line-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Signature of grant agreement:&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; February - March 2023</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:&#10;-.55pt;line-height:normal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:&#10;-.55pt;line-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">5.&nbsp;&nbsp; Proposal templates, guidance and model grant agreements (MGA):</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/erasmus/temp-form/af/af_erasmus-bb-lsii_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">&nbsp;Standard proposal template </a><br />\r\n</span><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/erasmus/wp-call/2022/call-fiche_erasmus-edu-2022-pol-exp-he_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; text-indent: 0px;\">Call document</a><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/erasmus/agr-contr/general-mga_erasmus_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"> Mono/Multi-beneficiary Model Grant Agreement</a></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>", "supportInfo": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\">For help related to this call, please contact: </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:red;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">please add a contact e-mail or url</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/portal/screen/support/faq;grantAndTendertype=1;categories=p_submission_eval;programme=null;actions=;keyword=;period=null\">Funding &amp; Tenders Portal FAQ</a></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\"> &nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ndash; Submission of proposals</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\">.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/portal/screen/support/helpdesks/contact-form\">IT Helpdesk</a></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\"> &nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&ndash; Contact the IT helpdesk for questions such as forgotten passwords, access rights and roles, technical aspects of submission of proposals, etc.</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&#10;&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;&#10;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;&#10;color:#595959;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:&#10;AR-SA\"><a href=\"https://webgate.ec.europa.eu/funding-tenders-opportunities/display/OM/Online+Manual\">Online Manual</a></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"> &nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#595959;mso-ansi-language:&#10;EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-bidi-font-weight:&#10;bold\">&ndash; Step-by-step online guide through the Portal processes from proposal preparation and submission to reporting on your on-going project. Valid for all 2021-2027 programmes.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>", "sepTemplate": "<p>To access the Electronic Submission Service, please click on the submission-button next to the <strong>type of action</strong> and the <strong>type of model grant agreement</strong> that corresponds to your proposal. You will then be asked to confirm your choice, as it cannot be changed in the submission system. Upon confirmation, you will be linked to the correct entry point.</p>\r\n<p>To access existing draft proposals for this topic, please login to the Funding &amp; Tenders Portal and select the My Proposals page of the My Area section.</p>", "links": [], "additionalDossiers": [], "infoPackDossiers": [], "callDetailsJSONItem": {"staticAdditionalInfo": "<p><em>European policy experimentations are transnational cooperation projects that involve testing the relevance, effectiveness, potential impact and scalability of activities through field trials in different countries. By combining strategic leadership, methodological soundness and a strong European dimension, they enable mutual learning and support evidence-based policy at European level.</em></p><p><em>The general objective of this call for proposals is to test and explore deeper transnational cooperation instruments to further develop a genuinely European dimension in the higher education sector, built on shared values, as mentioned in the European strategy for universities presented by the Commission on 18 January 2022 and as confirmed in the <a href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=OJ%3AJOC_2022_167_R_0003\">Council Conclusions on a European strategy empowering higher education institutions for the future of Europe</a> and the Council recommendation on building bridges for effective European higher education cooperation, adopted on 5 April 2022. The priority for this European policy experimentation call is to support partnerships of higher education institutions and relevant national, regional and/or HEI authorities to pilot:</em></p><ul level=\"0\"><li><em>a joint European degree label for joint transnational programmes responding to a number of co-created European criteria (Topic 1),</em></li> </ul><p><em>and/or</em></p><ul level=\"0\"><li><em>institutionalised cooperation EU instruments to explore the feasibility of establishing a possible legal status for alliances of higher education institutions at European level - such as \u2018European Universities\u2019 or any other type of alliance (Topic 2).</em></li> </ul>\n", "latestInfos": [{"approvalDate": "Jan 31, 2023 3:00:47 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Jan 31, 2023 3:00:47 PM", "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:normal;background:white\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:&#10;normal;background:white\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;&#10;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;padding:0cm;mso-ansi-language:EN-IE;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\">CALL EVALUATION RESULTS:</span></u></b><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:EN-IE;mso-fareast-language:&#10;EN-IE\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:&#10;normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:EN-IE;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\">Published: 15.06.2022<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:&#10;normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:EN-IE;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\">Deadline: 6.10.2022</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:&#10;normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:EN-IE;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:&#10;normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333;mso-ansi-language:EN-IE;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-IE\">Available budget for the call&nbsp;<b><span style=\"border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0cm;&#10;padding:0cm\">ERASMUS-EDU-2022-POL-EXP-HE</span></b>: EUR 2 000 000.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:&#10;normal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:&quo